reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 12, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars No glue on envelope
reviews.reviewText: Nice product. Envelopes a little larger then #10 and had to glue so I had to tape each one before mailing.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 16, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars Paper wrong size, no glue on non-standard envelopes
reviews.reviewText: I love the quality and design of this paper, but I'm returning it. Not only (as others have mentioned) is there no glue on the envelopes, but the envelopes are a non-standard type - they open at the end instead of with a flap on the back. Also, the paper is entirely the wrong size! It's NOT 8 1/2 X 11 US letter size paper! It's A4 paper. I can't use this for my purposes.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on March 23, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Beautiful paper but no glue on envelopes
reviews.reviewText: This writing set is very pretty! Fancy even. But it was my mistake thinking I was buying decorative typing paper and envelopes for mailing. The sheets are glued at top and you peel off as you need a sheet and then you can put it in the printer. There is no glue on envelopes, so to seal for mailing, I used a glue stick or scotch tape.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 24, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Well, this is another set of stationary where the envelopes have no adhesive at all. I don’t understand what is with companies who don’t put adhesive on their envelopes. How do they think we’re supposed to mail them.The paper and the envelopes are beautiful. But drops down to two stars when there’s no adhesive.I think they should have to put this in their description. I understand why they don’t. Because nobody would buy them.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 28, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Wish I had read the reviews before purchasing.Cheap, cheap, cheap !Flimsy paper, no glue on envelopes, odd size requiring extra postage!!
